originalText.text:
Ryan was very helpful throughout my first home purchasing process. He was knowledgeable, diligent, proactive, honest, and very accessible.

During the search, he diligently compiled a list of listings that he thought I would be interested in, while also searching for off-market options. He was readily available afterwards to gather feedback and better understand what I was looking for.

In the negotiation process, it was evident that he had earned the trust of the seller's agents. He very tactfully navigated through delicate topics, and I was able to end up getting a condo that I love at a price that I was comfortable with.

Throughout my search that spanned over a year and a half, I have gone through various different agents. It was no coincidence that Ryan was the last agent that finally got me all the way through closing. Would definitely recommend!

originalText.text: My wife and I decided to invest in a second home in NYC, so we reached out to Ryan.  He was very professional and patient with us. We weren’t all too familiar with the city and our options. This is where Ryan really came through. Very knowledgeable and provided great detail on the neighborhoods and what to consider in a building. We ended up closing on a great apartment on the Upper West Side.  Terrific negotiator with the seller too!  Highly recommend.
